headline: Eli Lilly's Obesity Drug Wins Approval In Sleep Apnea; Will ResMed Dive?
summary: Eli Lilly gained FDA approval late Friday for its weight-loss drug, Zepbound, as a treatment for obstructive sleep apnea.
